{"tid":1187584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得自己家姐係雞？","createTime":"2019-06-05T18:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T20:28:13.000Z","uid":199500,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"efb3ae1bbe701580c3021c39991d2e8605fdc508","tid":1187584,"uid":199500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T18:01:20.000Z","msg":"雖然係屋企人，但覺得自己家姐有時真係唔抵幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時玩下交友app ig約下人出街都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識親一個男朋友都會跟人地返屋企消失唔見左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要識左唔夠一陣就會上埋人地屋企住。<br />\n唔知比人中出幾多次，仲試過偷偷返黎屋企自己係廁所落仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到比條仔綠左，散左之後，又死死地氣返黎住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個循環已經持續到幾年。<br />\n有時係衣櫃搵衫又會無啦啦搵到佢d情趣內衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到我勁尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig d相既角度永遠都奇奇怪怪（就係因為咁先引到d麻甩佬約）<br />\n雖然有時真係睇唔過眼，但因為佢真係大我好大，所以唔夠膽批評佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時佢會同我呻d人話佢係雞好sad，雖然把口安慰佢，但其實都希望有一日佢可以真真正正仆一次街 改下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86902cbd45e645e5fcf44290c03fc89748f25df6","tid":1187584,"uid":144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f64f39b33ccefd2fac50b6a5dafff8aa2febd7","tid":1187584,"uid":8500,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T18:07:14.000Z","msg":"廁所落仔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e2549b32e348bba42f14faca771173dd7ec61d","tid":1187584,"uid":16061,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8